<h4>Final Design ✨</h4>

<h2>What is a Care Plan? And Why Do We Need It?</h2>

<p>Patients' interactions with doctors are short, sparse, and often reactive. As a result, doctors don't have enough information to provide holistic care. HealthTap partnered with a global health care provider to tackle this problem together.</p>

<p>A Care Plan is a guide designed by a medical provider for a patient to help that patient manage his or her condition. It can provide preventative measures, such as medication, measurements, and/or appointment reminders. It can also provide reactive measures, such as an alerting system for an emergency.</p>

